Second Department,

July, 1959

(July 14, 1959) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Jerry Robertson, Appellant, against Edward M. Fay, as Warden of Green Haven Prison, Respondent.

Motion for leave to appeal as a poor person and for other relief denied. Present — Nolan, P. J., Wenzel, Beldoek, Murphy and Ughetta, JJ.
